item.title: Weird Here to Help Halloween Special: Real Magic & Closing Down the Store (with John E. L. Tenney)
item.description: Steve Berg and Eric Edelstein are joined by paranormal investigator John E. L. Tenney for this special Halloween edition of Weird Here to Help, featuring a young witch who wants to follow in her mother's footsteps and a ghost story from the shadow of Mount Shasta. Feed: https://rss.art19.com/were-here-to-help

item.title: A Nightmare on My Street by DJ Jazzy Jeff & the Fresh Prince
item.description: In this special Halloween episode of THE STORY SONG PODCAST, your hosts review the 1988 hip hop hit, “A Nightmare on My Street” by DJ Jazzy Jeff & the Fresh Prince. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/thestorysongpodcast
